window.bookSummaryJSON = "Host Payne Lindsey investigates mysterious cold case disappearances with each new season of the hit true crime franchise Up and Vanished. From a missing South Georgia teacher, Tara Grinstead, which led to who arrests in season 1, to Kristal Reisinger, a young mother who disappeared from a remote Colorado mountain town in season 2, to the most recent case in season 3, the North West Montana disappearance of Ashley Loring HeavyRunner, an indigenous woman who went missing from the Blackfeet Nation Indian Reservation. As we prepare for season 4, check out the Up and Vanished spinoff series, The Vanishing Point, where the UAV team investigates several disappearances in Northern California's Hoopa Valley."; 
